quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  21,36,"Si yi'ii ma -an Nulaaﾉ熔- ﾉ兎e sirkooﾉ兎, ﾉ兎 jogitortaa ma si wanaa jalkitde hiﾉ兎 raﾉ熔ra jokkuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n wi'igol maﾉ橡兎: "Enee, ko oo woni yennude reweteeﾉ擁 mo'on ﾉ擁 wonﾉ熔n rewude ﾉ擁n?!" Hara ﾉ兎 jalnorte woni, ko ﾉ兎 yedduﾉ兎 ko Alla jippini kon e maﾉ橡兎 immorde ka Alqur'aanaare e ko O okki ﾉ兎 kon e neemaaji ko ﾉ兎 yeddu ﾉ兎; ko kamﾉ兎 hanndi e ayiibe on sabu hawtindirgol maﾉ橡兎 kala bone."
  21,37,"Neﾉ遼熔 on Tagaama e heﾃｱaare, kanko himo heﾃｱora piiji ﾉ擁n ado waﾉ蓉gol majji, ko sabu ﾉ蓉m si sirkooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n no heﾃｱara Lepte ﾉ容n, aray Mi holla on -onon heﾃｱorﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n Lepte Am ﾉ容n- ko heﾃｱornoﾉ熔n kon e ﾉ蓉m, wata on ﾉ預ﾉ橡砥 yaccinaneede ﾉ蓉m."
  21,38,"Heeferﾉ兎 yedduﾉ兎 Immital ﾉ兎n hiﾉ兎 wi'ude e noone heﾃｱorgol: "Ko honnde tuma ko foduﾉ熔n men kon laatotoo -ko onon yo Julﾉ兎- immorde e Immital si tawii ko on goonguﾉ兎 e kon ko nodditiﾉ熔n waﾉ蓉gol mum."
  21,39,"Sinndo ﾉ兎e heeferﾉ兎 yedduﾉ兎 Immital annduno tuma tawi ﾉ兎 ruttataa Yiite ngen gaayi geece maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n wanaa gaayi ﾉ殿bbe maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n kdai, wonnde kadi walloowo alaa mo no walla ﾉ兎 duﾃｱugol Lepte ﾉ容n gaayi maﾉ橡兎, sinndo ﾉ兎 yananano ﾉ蓉m ﾉ兎 heﾃｱortaano Lepte ﾉ容n."
  21,40,"Ngee Yiite nge ﾉ兎 leptetee e mu'un nge arataa e maﾉ橡兎 e anndal maﾉ橡兎, ko woni, nge aray e maﾉ橡兎 e juhayee, hara ﾉ兎 hattantaake yiltugol nge e maﾉ橡兎, wanaa kamﾉ兎 woni nennanoyteeﾉ兎 haa ﾉ兎 tuuba Hinnayee on hewta ﾉ兎."
  21,41,"Si tawii yimﾉ兎 maaﾉ預 ﾉ兎n jalkitii ma, haray wanaa an ﾉ蓉m fuﾉ遼熔ri, gomﾉ擁i jalkitanoo ma Nulaaﾉ兎 ado maaﾉ預 -an Nulaaﾉ熔- O huﾉ妬ndii yedduﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, ﾉ兎n laatinooﾉ兎 no jalkita ﾉ兎 Lepte ﾉ容n ﾉ兎n laatinooﾉ兎 no jalnora ﾉ兎 ka aduna tuma nde Nulaaﾉ兎 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎n hulﾉ妬nirta ﾉ兎."
  21,42,"Maakan -an Nulaaﾉ熔- ﾉ兎e heﾃｱorayﾉ兎 Lepte: "Ko hommbo reenata on jemma e ﾃｱalorma e kon ko Hinnorante On muuyani on immorde e jippinngol Lepte ﾉ容n e halkugol on?" ko woni, kamﾉ兎 gaayi jaﾅ逆aade waajuuji Joomi maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁n e hujjaaji Makko ﾉ擁n ko ﾉ兎 ﾉ蓉rniiﾉ兎, ﾉ兎 taskotaako hay e huunde e ﾉ蓉m sabu majjere e njofoyaagal."
  21,43,"Kaa no woodani ﾉ兎 reweteeﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 no dannda ﾉ兎 Lepte Amen ﾉ容n? ﾆ‘ hattantaake wallirde wonkiiji maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁n martinngol lorra e majji, ﾉ兎 anndantaa ﾉ擁 nafa, mo wallaali wonkii mun ko honno o wallirta tanaa makko?! wanaa kamﾉ兎 kadi woni walloyteeﾉ兎 immorde e Lepte Amen ﾉ容n."
  21,44,"Ko woni Men dakmitii ﾉ兎e yedduﾉ兎, Men dakmitiri baabiraaﾉ兎 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎n sabu ko Men weeﾉ妬tani ﾉ兎 immorde e neemaaji Amen; ka ﾉ預ynugol ﾉ兎, haa jamaanu ngun juutani ﾉ兎, ﾉ兎 hoditori ﾉ蓉m, ﾉ兎 ﾃｱiiﾉ妬 e geddi maﾉ橡兎. Kaa hara ﾉ兎e hoditorﾉ兎 neemaaji Amen heﾃｱorﾉ兎 Lepte Amen yi'aali wonnde Menen Meﾉ容n ara e leydi ndin Men uytira ndi e bannﾅ菊eji mayri doolnugol Amen yimﾉ兎 mayri, e Polgal Amen e hoore maﾉ橡兎, sakko ﾉ兎 taskoo ﾉ蓉m fii wata yanu e maﾉ橡兎 ko yani kon e tanaa maﾉ橡兎?! ﾆ‘e laataaki fooluﾉ兎, ko woni, kamﾉ兎 ko ﾉ兎 foolaaﾉ兎."